com%2Ftechorange%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2017%2F03%2F2017-03-20-2.09.16-1024x682.webp%3Fpng&h=fde5be09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 虛擬貨幣比特幣(Bitcoin)周五升至紀錄新高的4.8925萬美元之際，加拿大基金公司 Purpose 表示，監管機構已經批准該公司管理的比特幣場內交易基金(ETF)掛牌買賣。該基金將成為全球首隻比特幣ETF，令到散戶也可參與比特幣炒作熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大安大略省證券委員會(OSC)其後確認，批准有關 ETF 的運作。目前，散戶可以通過買賣比特幣期貨產品，以投資比特幣。不過，Purpose 的比特幣ETF 可以讓散戶變相直接持有比特幣，市場人士 Arthur Salzer稱，買賣比特幣ETF 對散戶而言，更具吸引力，因為ETF 是以資產淨值計算，不用支付溢價。<br />\n<br />\n美國基金業界人士 Todd Rosenbluth 表示，美國基金公司曾經申請成立比特幣ETF，但美國證券交易委員會(SEC)遲遲未批准。他相信，即使加國出現首隻比特幣ETF，相信正值人事更替的 SEC，也不大可能在短期內批准比特幣 ETF 面世。 (BC)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"GBTC算係咩?"},{"pid":"07bc858066a06026953e990c72a868563b55c304","tid":2406971,"uid":126348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"可以點買bitcoin?"},{"pid":"cc4c075ed3df75a70b3bdb764c215d51fb4440e2","tid":2406971,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"黎緊全世界都要走資避極權控制<br />\n只會升唔會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dda4eb5df26d6a3cc584bf3e01f2d50a0576fb5","tid":2406971,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34237e655293d4739676240890c44a75743f784e","tid":2406971,"uid":248351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d32ab718bdca0186365ac521fcdd992a09bf8073","tid":2406971,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b13427c103710c681f14be5a807acb4a954fa39","tid":2406971,"uid":351545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:23:10.000Z","msg":"係，但係都係有溢價，正常嚟講大規模嘅ETF唔會有咩溢價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一一次我見過有溢價係港股南方科指ETF，比人當係新股咁炒，但係都一日內回復翻正常水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />GBTC長期有"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"Gbtc嚴格黎講 應該唔算Bitcoin etf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"點解？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"Grayscale Bitcoin Trust（GBTC）是市場上首款Bitcoin信托基金，信託持有市面上約2%的Bitcoin。雖然它不是一隻Bitcoin ETF，但運作方式與商品ETF類似，以截稿時的數據計算，每股GBTC相等於0.00095524枚Bitcoin。<br />\n<br />\n上網quote既 <a href=\"https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/bitcoin-cryptocurrency-stock-ETF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planto.hk%2Fzh%2Fblog%2Fbitcoin-cryptocurrency-stock-ETF%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ8F7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=abf8b042\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/bitcoin-cryptocurrency-stock-ETF/</a>"},{"pid":"1d1bcb7b74fe3b5da26be2c4f019c45ea9c2cc6c","tid":2406971,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"個腦坐住咗？"}]}